{"_path":"/health/h012","_dir":"health","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"肝癌","description":null,"image":null,"sequence":12,"category":"養生防癌","link":null,"head":{"meta":[{"name":"keywords","content":""},{"name":"robots","content":""},{"name":"author","content":""},{"name":"copyright","content":"© 2024 A7新林口 - 社區網站"},{"name":"og:title","content":"健康休閒"}]},"publishedAt":"2025-04-17T00:00:00.000Z","toc":true,"body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"肝癌"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"肝癌"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"什麼是肝癌"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"什麼是肝癌？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"肝癌（Hepatocellular Carcinoma, HCC）是起源於肝臟細胞（主要為肝細胞）的惡性腫瘤，是最常見的原發性肝臟癌症。肝癌通常與慢性肝病密切相關，如肝硬化、慢性 B 型或 C 型肝炎、脂肪肝或長期酗酒。其他風險因素包括黃麴毒素暴露、糖尿病、肥胖及遺傳疾病（如血色素沉著症）。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"症狀"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：早期常無明顯症狀，晚期可能出現腹痛、腹脹、黃疸、食慾下降、體重減輕、疲倦或腹水。\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"診斷"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：透過血液檢查（甲胎蛋白 AFP）、超音波、CT、MRI 或活檢確診。\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"治療"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：根據分期（I-IV 期）與肝功能，治療包括手術切除、肝移植、局部消融（如射頻消融）、動脈化療栓塞（TACE）、標靶治療或免疫療法。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"hr","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"如何預防肝癌"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"如何預防肝癌？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"預防肝癌的關鍵在於降低慢性肝病風險及減少致癌因素暴露："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ol","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"預防與治療肝炎"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"接種 B 型肝炎疫苗（新生兒及高風險成人）。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"篩檢 B 型或 C 型肝炎，若感染應積極治療（如抗病毒藥物可控制 B 肝或治癒 C 肝）。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"避免共用針頭、確保醫療器具消毒，降低血液傳播風險。"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"限制酒精攝取"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"避免過量飲酒，男性每日酒精攝取不超過 20-30g（約 2 杯啤酒），女性不超過 10-20g。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"長期酗酒者應尋求戒酒支持。"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"控制脂肪肝"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"保持健康體重（BMI 18.5-24.9），避免肥胖。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"透過健康飲食與運動預防非酒精性脂肪肝病（NAFLD），因其可能進展為肝硬化或肝癌。"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"健康飲食"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"避免攝取受黃麴毒素污染的食物（如發霉的穀物、花生、玉米），尤其在熱帶地區。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"多吃新鮮蔬果、全穀類，減少加工食品及高糖高脂飲食。"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"管理代謝疾病"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"控制糖尿病、高血脂、高血壓，這些疾病與肝癌風險增加相關。"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"避免環境毒素"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"減少接觸化學致癌物（如農藥、工業溶劑）。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"飲用乾淨水源，避免污染。"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"定期篩檢"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"高風險族群（如 B/C 肝患者、肝硬化患者、長期酗酒者）應每 6 個月進行肝臟超音波與 AFP 檢查，早期發現腫瘤。"}]}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"hr","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"如何保養針對肝癌患者或高風險者"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"如何保養（針對肝癌患者或高風險者）？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"若已診斷肝癌或屬高風險族群，保養重點在於減緩疾病進展、保護肝功能及提升生活品質："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ol","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"遵循醫療計畫"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"配合醫囑進行手術、局部治療、標靶治療（如 Sorafenib、Lenvatinib）或免疫療法。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"定期追蹤影像學檢查（CT/MRI）與血液檢查（AFP、肝功能）。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"及早報告症狀（如腹痛、黃疸、腹水）以調整治療。"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"保護肝臟"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"完全戒酒"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：酒精會加重肝臟損傷，必須避免。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"避免不必要藥物或補充劑，某些物質可能損害肝臟，服用前諮詢醫師。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"避免食用生或未煮熟的食物（如生魚片），降低感染風險。"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"營養支持"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"均衡飲食"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：採用低脂、高纖飲食，攝取優質蛋白（如魚、雞蛋、豆製品）以支持肝臟修復。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"控制鹽分"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：每日鈉攝取低於 2300mg，避免腹水或水腫。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"小份多餐"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：若食慾下降，可分 5-6 餐進食，選擇易消化食物（如粥、蒸蔬菜）。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"補充維生素"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：若有營養缺乏（如維生素 D、K），可在醫師指導下補充。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"避免高糖高脂"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：減少甜點、油炸食品，防止脂肪肝惡化。"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"適度運動"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"根據體能進行輕度運動（如散步、伸展、太極），每周 150 分鐘中等強度活動，改善體力與代謝。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"避免過度勞累，特別在治療期間。"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"管理併發症"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"若有腹水或黃疸，遵循醫囑控制飲食與水分攝取。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"預防肝性腦病，減少高蛋白飲食（若有腦病風險）並遵醫囑用藥。"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"心理健康"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"肝癌診斷可能帶來情緒壓力，建議參與支持團體、心理諮詢或冥想。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"與家人保持聯繫，尋求情感支持。"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"預防感染"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"接種流感疫苗、肺炎鏈球菌疫苗，降低感染風險。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"保持個人衛生，避免接觸傳染源。"}]}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"hr","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"具體飲食建議"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"具體飲食建議"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"早餐"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：燕麥粥搭配蘋果片、奇亞籽，配無糖豆漿。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"午餐"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：糙米飯、蒸鱈魚、燙青江菜，佐以少許橄欖油。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"晚餐"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：雞胸肉蔬菜湯（南瓜、胡蘿蔔）、藜麥沙拉。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"點心"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：無鹽核桃、新鮮橙子或奇異果。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"飲品"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：多喝水、綠茶（適量），避免含糖飲料及酒精。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"注意"}]},{"type":"text","value":"："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"若有腹水，限制液體與鹽分攝取，具體方案需諮詢醫師。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"若接受化療或標靶治療，根據副作用（如噁心）調整飲食，選擇清淡食物。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"hr","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"其他注意事項"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"其他注意事項"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"高風險族群"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：B/C 肝患者、肝硬化患者應終身監控，即使病毒控制良好，肝癌風險仍存在。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"早期診斷關鍵"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：早期肝癌（I 期）手術切除後 5 年存活率可達 70-80%，因此定期篩檢至關重要。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"謹慎補充劑"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：某些草藥或保健品（如含高劑量維生素 A）可能損肝，需經醫師評估。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"家族病史"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：若有肝癌家族史，應告知醫師，加強篩檢頻率。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"透過健康生活、積極治療及定期檢查，可有效降低肝癌風險或改善預後。若已確診，與醫療團隊密切合作並調整生活方式，能提升生活品質與存活機會。"}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"肝癌","depth":2,"text":"肝癌","children":[{"id":"什麼是肝癌","depth":3,"text":"什麼是肝癌？"},{"id":"如何預防肝癌","depth":3,"text":"如何預防肝癌？"},{"id":"如何保養針對肝癌患者或高風險者","depth":3,"text":"如何保養（針對肝癌患者或高風險者）？"},{"id":"具體飲食建議","depth":3,"text":"具體飲食建議"},{"id":"其他注意事項","depth":3,"text":"其他注意事項"}]}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:health:h012.md","_source":"content","_file":"health/h012.md","_extension":"md"}